### Finance API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Create Pending Purchase
POST {{baseUrl}}/purchase/pending/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "payment_method": "online"
}

### 2. Finalize Purchase (After Payment)
POST {{baseUrl}}/purchase/final/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "transaction_id": 1
}

### 3. Verify Purchase (Owner only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/purchase/verify/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "buyer_code": "123456"
}

### 4. Get User Purchases
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/purchases/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Purchase Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/purchases/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get User Wallet (Owner only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/wallet/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get Wallet Transactions (Owner only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/wallet/transactions/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Admin Wallet (Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/admin-wallet/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get Admin Transactions (Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/admin-transactions/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Get All Transactions (Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/transactions/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Get Transaction Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/transactions/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
